{
  "stem": "11723.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 118.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They should just go to all the Red Cross homes and see if we are in any one of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they found us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And they were taking us back home, which was great reunion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was fantastic to see my mother again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And as we were crossing the bridge, at the bridgehead, there were Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the Russians love kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They just adore kids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They may be raping women, but kids, they love.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they gave each of us a loaf of bread-- my sister one and I got one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "My sister ate that bread so fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "She just-- one minute, it was here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "One minute, [LAUGHS] it disappeared in that little person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "She got so sick that she-- under normal circumstances, she would have had to gone-- be taken to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "But my mother didn't want to take her to the hospital, because she said conditions weren't that great in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "She didn't want her to get something else, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And-- they took her to a doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And somehow they gave her something and she was OK later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after that, of course, my mother deloused us and tried to nurse us back to health, which was very difficult because we both had TB.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And I'm so surprised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I was so full of ringworm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "But by some miracle, I only have one scar [LAUGHS] on my wrist, which isn't a big deal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And at this point, this is 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "People were trickling back who survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And the first one who came back was my grandpa on my mother's side, Grandpa Gluck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "But he was in such bad condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "He was practically beaten to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "He was paralyzed on one side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "He lost the power of speech.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
